  <text x="20" y="32" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Project Keystone — Progmat's Corda-to-Avalanche Migration Snapshot</text>
  <g font-family="sans-serif">
    <rect x="30" y="55" width="640" height="140" rx="10" fill="#1c1c1e" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="1.2"/>
    <text x="50" y="82" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Timeline</text>
    <text x="50" y="108" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">2019 — Progmat launches on Corda 5 (led by MUFG)</text>
    <text x="50" y="132" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">May 2026 — JGB tokenization working group launched</text>
    <text x="50" y="156" fill="#67e8f9" font-size="13" font-weight="700">Jul 13, 2026 — Avalanche L1 migration complete (Project Keystone)</text>
    <text x="50" y="180" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">Oct 2026 (expected) — JGB working group findings due</text>

    <text x="50" y="228" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Migration Scale &amp; Performance Change</text>
    <text x="50" y="254" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Assets migrated</text>
    <rect x="290" y="241" width="330" height="18" rx="3" fill="#e84142"/>
    <text x="628" y="254" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-weight="700">¥452B</text>
    <text x="50" y="284" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Settlement finality</text>
    <text x="290" y="284" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-weight="700">Under 2 seconds</text>
    <text x="50" y="310" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Ownership-transfer speed</text>
    <text x="290" y="310" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-weight="700">3-5x faster</text>
    <text x="50" y="335" fill="#71717a" font-size="12">Source: Progmat, Avalanche blog, The Block</text>

    <rect x="30" y="365" width="640" height="150" rx="10" fill="#1e2a3a" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.3"/>
    <text x="50" y="392" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Progmat Ownership (Major Shareholders)</text>
    <text x="50" y="418" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">MUFG 49% · NTT Data 13.5%</text>
    <text x="50" y="442" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Sumitomo Mitsui Bank, Mizuho, Sumitomo Mitsui Trust 7.5% each</text>
    <text x="50" y="466" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Tokyo Stock Exchange (JPX) 5% · SBI PTS Holdings 5% · Datachain 5%</text>
    <text x="50" y="495" fill="#71717a" font-size="12">Supports 45 of Japan's 89 public security-token projects (53.4% of deals, 64.6% of value)</text>

    <rect x="30" y="535" width="640" height="120" rx="10" fill="#2a1414" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.3"/>
    <text x="50" y="562" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="14" font-weight="700">What's Still Unproven</text>
    <text x="50" y="587" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Whether EVM compatibility actually draws outside on-chain capital</text>
    <text x="50" y="611" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">JGB pilot only firms up after Oct 2026 working-group findings</text>
    <text x="50" y="635" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Could just repeat the same closed institutional loop, on faster rails</text>
  </g>
</svg>
<p style="font-size:11px;color:#52525b;margin-top:-10px">Figures are approximate, based on public press releases and news reports, and may differ from real-time data.</p>
